IMAPAccount fastmail
Host imap.fastmail.com
Port 993
AuthMechs LOGIN
User kimsaram32@fastmail.com
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only -d ~/.authinfo.gpg | awk -F ' ' '/kimsaram32@fastmail.com/ { print $(NF-2); exit; }'"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore fastmail-remote
Account fastmail

MaildirStore fastmail-local
Path ~/mail/
Inbox ~/mail/INBOX
Trash ~/mail/Trash
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel fastmail
Far :fastmail-remote:
Near :fastmail-local:
Patterns *
Expunge None
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
Create Near
SyncState *
